itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T17:50:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細佬我嚟緊11月會同女朋友去大阪，想住心齋橋附近，筆直一晚千五蚊左右，有無邊間酒店推介下呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前住過，「難波東方酒店」，係千日前，行過去心齋橋5-10mins既事，去黑門市場，5分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f913961b8b8c72a303c248fec228bab8d6d1653","tid":424473,"uid":70789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T17:56:42.000Z","msg":"The cross hotel"},{"pid":"f5fcff8ed197a4a2c71b65522aac352c80fff7ad","tid":424473,"uid":130963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T18:17:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>The cross hotel</blockquote><br />\n心目中都係呢間，但係full哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2946fe809ac5620371881d57bc9da789fbe8180a","tid":424473,"uid":54432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T19:04:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千五蚊晚酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如住平d 食左去好過</blockquote><br />\n之前住Via Inn Shinsaibashi平靚正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bacf3a43338ce8e462e35c8a1ffedb214412771","tid":424473,"uid":100635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"E個預算大把選擇"},{"pid":"ad21a6a6937c09e99becc62dcf1ad64d6090f3a0","tid":424473,"uid":130963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:41:09.000Z","msg":"個個都話大把選擇，鳩揀都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾d名嚟好喎"},{"pid":"339e9e8eb4f2f36543dd9683cd8c9508804a0c20","tid":424473,"uid":70448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08: